We accept returns or exchanges within 14 days of receiving the purchase, provided it is in unworn, unwashed condition with all tags and labels attached.

Terms and Conditions Apply.

Click here to view our full Returns and Exchanges Policy for complete details.

We see you slaying in our gorgeous hipster bikini. This high-waisted sporty bottom provides full coverage, athletic styling with maximum comfort, and creates a flattering silhouette. Made from high-quality, stretchy fabric with UV 50+ properties, it creates a barely-there touch with good protection. You'll look fabulous and feel even better in this summer-perfect swim staple while lounging in the sun.

THE EXCLUSIVE PLACEMENT OF THE PRINT HIGHLIGHTS THE ORIGINALITY OF THE DESIGN.

MADE IN USA.

*** Multiple tops available ***

Your order will be shipped in 1 to 7 business days (depending on the items in your order). In most cases from order to delivery takes between 1-2 weeks.

*Sometimes international orders might take a bit longer to be delivered.

If you need an EXPEDITED SHIPPING please contact us via chat, email us at support@pineappleclothing.com or call us (800) 561-7008 and we will make sure you receive your order on time!
